  The $(LINK2 $(ROOT_DIR)overview.html, overview) page gives a feel for
  the unique features of the language.
  )

  $(P
  $(LINK2 http://ddili.org/ders/d.en/index.html, $(B Programming in D)) is an
  extensive tutorial by Ali Ã‡ehreli and a great starting point for absolute
  beginners. It doesn't assume that you know any other programming languages,
